<text id="02-output-contract" title="Prompt A/B Power Calculator Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="700" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the power-calc-spec artefact + valid/invalid examples + forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/prompt-ab-power-calculator.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["artefact_id", "owner", "trigger", "baseline_rate", "mde", "alpha", "power", "traffic_per_day", "per_arm_n", "inputs_used", "version", "last_reviewed"],
  "properties": {
    "artefact_id": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-z0-9-]{3,64}$"},
    "owner": {"type": "string", "minLength": 3, "not": {"enum": ["team", "we", "us", "engineering"]}},
    "trigger": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["kind", "value"],
      "properties": {"kind": {"enum": ["event", "threshold", "schedule"]}, "value": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2}}
    },
    "baseline_rate": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.0, "maximum": 1.0, "exclusiveMinimum": 0.0, "exclusiveMaximum": 1.0},
    "mde": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.001, "maximum": 0.5},
    "alpha": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.001, "maximum": 0.2},
    "power": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.5, "maximum": 0.99},
    "traffic_per_day": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1},
    "per_arm_n": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 10},
    "inputs_used": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "required": ["name", "source"]}, "minItems": 3},
    "version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9]+\\.[0-9]+\\.[0-9]+$"},
    "last_reviewed": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}$"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item id="f1">trigger.value contains "when needed" / "as required" / "ad hoc"</item>
      <item id="f2">baseline_rate or mde missing a source citation in inputs_used</item>
      <item id="f3">alpha &gt; 0.2 (false-positive ceiling)</item>
      <item id="f4">power &lt; 0.5 (under-powered)</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "ab-support-greeting-2026q2",
  "owner": "ruslan@faion.net",
  "trigger": {"kind": "schedule", "value": "weekly: thursday"},
  "baseline_rate": 0.62,
  "mde": 0.04,
  "alpha": 0.05,
  "power": 0.8,
  "traffic_per_day": 1200,
  "per_arm_n": 2350,
  "inputs_used": [
    {"name": "baseline_eval", "source": "git://faion/eval/q2-baseline.json"},
    {"name": "mde_target", "source": "git://faion/product/q2-targets.md"},
    {"name": "traffic_analytics", "source": "warehouse://analytics.daily_traffic"}
  ],
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "last_reviewed": "2026-05-22"
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "x",
  "owner": "team",
  "trigger": {"kind": "event", "value": "when needed"},
  "baseline_rate": 1.5,
  "mde": -0.1,
  "alpha": 0.3,
  "power": 0.3,
  "traffic_per_day": 0,
  "per_arm_n": 5,
  "inputs_used": [],
  "version": "v1",
  "last_reviewed": "yesterday"
}
]]></code>
    <note>owner=team; trigger 'when needed' (f1); baseline_rate out of range; mde negative; alpha &gt;0.2 (f3); power &lt;0.5 (f4); traffic 0; n too small; inputs empty (f2).</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-prompt-ab-power-calculator.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
